assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Ju-Kao Engineering Co., Ltd. engages in the construction of large-scale projects in Taiwan and internationally. It undertakes factory steel structures, machinery, large storage tanks, pipelines, utility devices, and environmental protection equipment projects. The company is also involved in the installation, repairing, and maintenance of mechanical equipment, including diesel power generators, fans and blowers, turbines, chemical machinery, and various types of cranes; maching of mechanical components; and design, fabrication, and installation engineering of industrial factory and mechanical equipment, as well as heavy-duty machinery. In addition, it engages in the design and construction of power substation and cabling; design, installation, and maintenance of automatic control systems; engineering of air conditioning, cooling towers, and fire protection systems; and building construction, hydraulic engineering, and survey and exploration of the earth works. Further, the company operates in SRC building, floating dock, and harbor's construction areas; constructs dust collection, conveying, air pollution control, noise control, hydraulic machinery and pumping, and water and waste water treatment systems, as well as crane equipment; fabricates and pipes oil tanks, storage tanks, and pressure vessels; and undertakes metal painting and coating projects, as well as civil engineering - survey and exploration of earth work. Ju-Kao Engineering Co., Ltd. was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Kaohsiung City, Taiwan.
